29:57.603 --> 30:00.003
He insulted my date, Nadia!

30:01.140 --> 30:03.768
-Oh, my God.
-Go back to your seat.

30:04.010 --> 30:06.638
-She can't talk?
-They're our guests.

30:06.846 --> 30:11.215
-I just asked about the necklace.
