concubine stuff from anybody.

31:21.287 --> 31:24.586
-I no speak English!
-You a California resident?

31:24.791 --> 31:27.988
-I no speak English!
-Know what you're entitled?

31:28.194 --> 31:29.957
I no speak English!

31:30.196 --> 31:35.600
