32:40.900 --> 32:43.892
I only wish we were in the Army...

32:44.103 --> 32:48.597
-...so I could have you shot.
-Yes, sir.

32:50.343 --> 32:51.503
Twice.

32:55.147 --> 32:57.980
That was so much fun!

32:58.451 --> 33:02.581
My face is numb.
What do you wanna do now?

33:03.322 --> 33:06.587
There's a party down the street.
Let's go!

33:06.826 --> 33:12.230
