-Who cares?

33:33.686 --> 33:37.679
I'm driving 55 miles an hour, here!
Will you, for chri--

33:38.190 --> 33:39.555
Stop it!

33:48.134 --> 33:52.468
-Stop, please!
-You're frowning again.

33:52.705 --> 33:57.108
Stop it! For chrissakes,
there's a car behind us!

33:57.310 --> 33:59.073
Gotta do better than that.

33:59.378 --> 34:02.905
