35:02.208 --> 35:04.039
Walter, what--

35:12.284 --> 35:15.515
You son of a bitch, I'll kill you!

35:16.022 --> 35:17.990
Damn bastard!

35:29.402 --> 35:34.305
Jesus, that guy's a maniac.
He was really trying to kill me.

35:34.740 --> 35:36.367
Why'd you break up?

35:36.575 --> 35:40.306
You must be the best match
since Bonnie and Clyde.

35:50.189 --> 35:52.180
Come on.

35:53.893 --> 35:55.087
I'm sorry.

35:56.829 --> 35:59.059
I really am. I...

36:00.099 --> 36:01.760
