36:22.321 --> 36:24.448
Do you have a Kleenex?

36:27.193 --> 36:29.024
A handkerchief?

36:32.565 --> 36:33.827
Here.

36:35.367 --> 36:38.302
I hate it when my eyes get all puffy.

36:38.537 --> 36:42.166
