36:44.677 --> 36:46.736
Are my eyes puffy?

36:50.382 --> 36:54.045
Can we stop so I can blow my nose
and wash my face?

36:54.253 --> 36:56.585
I gotta go to the bathroom.

36:56.822 --> 36:59.052
Yeah, sure. Okay.

37:00.993 --> 37:02.153
