39:37.650 --> 39:40.312
I'm looking for my date.

39:40.519 --> 39:44.478
She's a brunette with a red dress on,
really pretty.

39:44.690 --> 39:49.525
And she came in
the bathroom here and, see--

39:49.728 --> 39:52.925
