40:20.392 --> 40:21.950
Can I buy you a drink?

40:22.227 --> 40:26.960
She had a thing with her ex,
and she got a little emotional.

40:27.199 --> 40:31.033
She started crying and wanted
to stop at a gas station.

40:31.236 --> 40:33.204
So we stopped next door.

40:33.439 --> 40:37.705
She took a long time.
When I went to get her, she'd left.

40:37.910 --> 40:42.870
The guy said she came here.
She probably went into this bathroom.

40:43.082 --> 40:48.486
It wasn't like I was trying to
look in. I was trying to find her.

40:48.821 --> 40:51.221
Come dance with me.

40:51.890 --> 40:55.951
-This is the girl. Right here.
-Five dollars, please.

41:00.733 --> 41:05.295
-I know you're a good dancer.
-No, I really don't wanna dance.

41:06.972 --> 41:10.669
-Stop, it's not funny.
-Come on.

41:10.976 --> 41:13.103
I'm sorry.

41:15.481 --> 41:17.449
Let's just go.

41:18.317 --> 41:21.480
Please. I'm sorry.

42:28.353 --> 42:30.878
All right, you ready for this?

42:40.933 --> 42:43.265
-Let's go now.
-Please, Walter.

43:14.399 --> 43:18.802
-Hi, I just wanted to come by and--
-David, don't--

43:19.037 --> 43:23.633
I came by to apologize.
I still love her very much.

43:23.842 --> 43:27.403
What? So you can drill her?
You son of a bitch!

43:39.725 --> 43:41.955
You bitch!

43:46.231 --> 43:48.358
We're leaving. Now!

43:52.905 --> 43:55.840
You son of a bitch!

44:04.316 --> 44:07.308
Let's go before the cops show up.

44:08.754 --> 44:10.813
Come on, come on!

44:12.324 --> 44:14.383
Move it, move it, move it.

44:16.995 --> 44:19.361
Get in. Get in!

44:20.332 --> 44:21.492
How much?

44:21.733 --> 44:23.826
-Cash or plastic?
-Cash!

44:24.036 --> 44:27.164
It's $17.50.
What's going on over there?

44:27.372 --> 44:30.432
I wanna talk to you.
Get out of the car.

44:30.676 --> 44:33.167
Just get out of the--

44:34.246 --> 44:37.704
Get back inside, you stupid idiot!

44:50.862 --> 44:55.265
Your ex's hobby is killing people.
What's his profession?

44:56.068 --> 45:00.630
-He's a defence lawyer.
