45:19.558 --> 45:22.118
I'm not taking you to any party!

45:22.327 --> 45:23.988
Party!

45:25.831 --> 45:28.391
I'm gonna take you home.

45:28.734 --> 45:30.099
To Baton Rouge?

45:31.670 --> 45:35.936
I'm taking you to your friends' house.
Where do they live?

45:36.308 --> 45:40.836
-We have to get on the freeway.
-No! No more freeways.

45:41.580 --> 45:44.845
It's the only way I know
how to get there.

45:46.285 --> 45:51.154
-What's the exact address?
-I know the house.

45:56.662 --> 45:59.756
-I'm getting on the freeway.
-Where's the hole?

45:59.965 --> 46:02.695
But if you make one move--
You listening?

46:02.934 --> 46:05.960
If you make one move
that makes me nervous...

46:06.171 --> 46:10.130
