intersection. Understand?

46:10.542 --> 46:12.533
Don't frown, Walter.

46:13.879 --> 46:17.645
Here's the house. Right....

46:19.384 --> 46:22.842
Okay, here, stop. Right here.

46:31.163 --> 46:34.724
When was the last time
you saw these people?

46:34.933 --> 46:36.924
About six years.

46:37.436 --> 46:38.664
Listen to me.

46:38.904 --> 46:41.737
Listen. Listen to me.

46:42.174 --> 46:45.143
You absolutely sure this is the house?

46:45.344 --> 46:47.335
Absolutely.

46:49.448 --> 46:51.109
Jesus!

47:02.194 --> 47:07.632
Hey! Stop! Get out of there!
Come here a minute!

47:17.976 --> 47:19.876
Your beautiful car.

47:23.548 --> 47:27.951
Look at the bright side.
What the hell else could happen?

47:34.559 --> 47:38.154
-Nadia, just stay out of this.
-Shut up, bitch!

47:38.397 --> 47:39.887
Your wallet.

47:41.967 --> 47:45.801
-Oh, shit! The cops!
-Drop the gun!

47:51.343 --> 47:53.311
There was three girls.

47:53.512 --> 47:58.347
One of the girls put a gun to my head!
She had a knife in my crotch!

47:58.617 --> 48:01.313
Get out of the freaking car!

48:01.620 --> 48:04.589
One had red hair standing straight up.

48:04.790 --> 48:08.624
