and one had a big tattoo!

48:11.763 --> 48:14.459
How much did you drink tonight, sir?

48:38.023 --> 48:39.320
Good.

48:39.791 --> 48:41.383
Head back.

48:41.860 --> 48:43.691
Eyes closed.

48:43.895 --> 48:45.795
Arms out.

48:45.997 --> 48:47.794
Palms up.

48:47.999 --> 48:51.491
