touch the tip of your nose.

48:52.070 --> 48:53.298
Good.

48:53.505 --> 48:55.530
Now the other hand.

48:57.742 --> 49:00.404
Now, keep your eyes closed.

49:00.645 --> 49:04.513
Raise your right foot
eight inches for 10 seconds.

49:16.127 --> 49:18.994
God, I feel horrible.

49:19.631 --> 49:22.293
Dare I hope that you sobered up?

49:22.834 --> 49:25.325
Oh, I drank. I drank so much.

49:26.505 --> 49:28.405
Yes, you did.

49:30.275 --> 49:34.177
And the dinner party.... Oh, God.

49:34.412 --> 49:37.347
-Walter, I'm so sorry.
-Well...

49:37.816 --> 49:40.444
