49:44.990 --> 49:48.619
I just have this chemical imbalance.

49:48.827 --> 49:54.129
It's like an allergy to alcohol.
It makes me crazy, that's all.

49:54.966 --> 49:56.263
Is that so?

49:58.336 --> 50:03.433
Look, Walter, I know you hate me.
So just listen.

50:04.109 --> 50:07.135
Take me to my friend Cathy's house.

50:07.679 --> 50:12.207
I know the address.
I won't ever bother you again.

50:17.022 --> 50:19.013
I'll kill you!

50:19.257 --> 50:20.519
Great!

50:20.725 --> 50:24.252
-I thought we'd lost him!
-What fun would that be?

50:25.997 --> 50:27.760
-David!
-Hold the tray!

50:37.876 --> 50:42.108
You son of a bitch! You wanna play?
Fine, I'll kill you!

50:53.625 --> 50:57.721
Actually, if you'll just
drop me off at the nearest hotel--

50:57.929 --> 51:02.696
