51:25.557 --> 51:29.653
My friends are nice, quiet people.
They'll bore you.

51:29.861 --> 51:33.160
We'll just have to
liven them up, won't we?

51:42.407 --> 51:44.500
Seen some traffic, pal?

51:46.611 --> 51:49.341
-Walter, listen to me.
-What?

51:49.581 --> 51:51.572
Party pooper.

51:55.720 --> 51:58.280
-Please, Walter.
-This is great.

52:03.461 --> 52:06.794
-How are you?
-Walter Davis, rocket scientist.

52:08.466 --> 52:10.127
