53:16.067 --> 53:17.694
Boston fans?

53:17.902 --> 53:20.268
Do I hear a mambo?

53:20.572 --> 53:21.903
Come on, Nadia.

53:25.009 --> 53:27.569
It's mambo time!

53:30.515 --> 53:32.574
Listen to me!

53:37.255 --> 53:40.088
Come and dance with me, darling.

53:49.267 --> 53:51.758
Walter Davis, brain surgeon.

53:52.637 --> 53:55.538
Walter Davis, mambo king!

53:57.776 --> 54:01.644
-Mambo with me, darling!
-Would you care for another--

54:04.949 --> 54:08.441
